snippet.title: PRIN-C1 Gameplay Trailer: Unleash Your Inner Runner!
snippet.description:
Dive into the thrilling world of PRIN-C1 with our exciting gameplay trailer! This video showcases the stunning graphics and immersive gameplay made possible by the powerful Godot Engine, specifically utilizing the capabilities of Godot 4. Whether you're a seasoned game developer or a fan of the gamedev community, this trailer highlights the potential of Godot 3D in creating captivating gaming experiences. Don't miss out on the action-watch now to see what makes PRIN-C1 a must-play title!

Synopsis: An endless runner where you are a flipping bulldog!

Run, trot and jump as you collect treats while avoiding speed blockers, pits and enemies. Unlock fun costumes by completing score.

Available on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2610970/PRINC1/
